---
title: Lentil Veggie Chilli with Zesty Rice
description: When it comes to creating deliciously simple vegetarian recipes, Chef Mimi rarely gets it wrong. Packed with fresh, colourful veg, her take on this classic Veggie Chilli won’t disappoint. Packed with lentils and kidney beans and finished off with a tomato and coriander salsa and dollop of soured cream.
